USER-ROLE: INSERT INTO user_role (roleName, description, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
USER: INSERT INTO user (userName, password, userRoleId, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
ACCOUNT-TYPE: INSERT INTO account_type (accountTypeName, description, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES(?, ?, ?, ?)
TRANSACTION-TYPE: INSERT INTO transaction_type (displayName, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES(?, ?, ?)
TENANT: INSERT INTO tenant (tenantName, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES(?, ?, ?)
BANK: INSERT INTO bank (name, externalId, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES(?, ?, ?, ?)
ACCOUNT: INSERT INTO account (displayName, accountTypeId, tenantId, bankId, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
CATEGORY-TYPE: INSERT INTO category_type (categoryTypeName, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?)
CATEGORY: INSERT INTO category (categoryTypeId, categoryName, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
SUBCATEGORY: INSERT INTO subcategory (subcategoryName, categoryId, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
PAYEE: INSERT INTO payee (payeeName, defaultSubCategoryId, createdById, lastModifiedById) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
IMPORT-TRASACTION: INSERT INTO transaction (tenantId, typeId, transactionAmount, transactionDate, payeeId, reconciled, categoryId, subCategoryId, createdById, lastModifiedById) SELECT ?, tt.id, ?, ?, p.id, ?, c.id, sc.id, u.id, u.id FROM transaction_type tt JOIN payee as p ON p.payeeName = ? JOIN subcategory as sc ON sc.id = p.defaultSubCategoryId JOIN category as c ON sc.categoryId = c.id JOIN user as u on u.username = ? WHERE tt.displayName = ?
